description: The Deka EURO iSTOXX ex Fin Dividend+ UCITS ETF is a UCITS IV-compliant mutual fund that replicates the performance of the EURO iSTOXX ex Financials High Dividend 50 Price Index (Price Index). The index includes the 50 EURO STOXX ex Financials companies with the highest dividend yields from the Eurozone. The index components are weighted accordingly based on dividends.
name: Deka EURO iSTOXX ex Fin Dividend+ UCITS ETF
